<HEADLINE> Guinean Party Congratulates Jiang on Re-election </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 24 (Xinhua) -- The Guinean Parti de L'unite
et du Progress (PUP) has congratulated Jiang Zemin on his
re-election as general secretary of the Central Committee of the
Communist Party of China (CPC).
</P>
<P>
The 15th National Congress of the CPC accepted unanimously Deng
Xiaoping Theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, said PUP general secretary Aboubacar Sompare on
behalf of Guinean head of state and PUP president Lansana Conte.
</P>
<P>
Applying the Chinese people's rich experience in culture and
technology, the CPC's new collective leadership will lead China
smoothly to the 21st century and help it become an economy magnet
in the modern world, Sompare added.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese people will surely accomplish the sacred task of
unifying the motherland, because following Hong Kong's return,
Macau will do the same and Taiwan will be reunified with the
motherland, Sompare believed. 
</P>
</TEXT>
