<HEADLINE> Drafting of 15th Party Congress Report (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
During the week-long congress, all delegates and Party members
agreed that the decision to hold high the great banner of Deng
Xiaoping Theory reflects the will of the Party, the army and the
people.
