relations with African countries and has provided as much
assistance as possible in Africa's struggle for national
independence and liberation.
</P>
<P>
In recent years, he said, President Jiang Zemin, Premier Li
Peng and Zhu himself have visited Africa, and China is ready to
strengthen its unity and friendship with African countries and
promote co-operation with Africa.
</P>
<P>
Tevoedjre said Benin believes that China is an important force
in the international community, and Benin thanks it for its
help. He said that China has made noticeable progress in its
reform and opening-up drive in recent years, from which Benin and
other African nations can learn.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the hope that China will play an even greater role
in Africa.
</P>
<P>
Tevoedjre arrived here earlier today as a guest of China's
Foreign Ministry. 
</P>
</TEXT>
