committee which will meet every three years.
</P>
<P>
Modise was quoted as saying that strong ties were developing
and the agreement with Togo was seen "as building bridges between
southern and west Africa".
</P>
<P>
If Togo wanted to buy military equipment from South Africa,
its request would be considered, Modise said. 
