<HEADLINE> Gremio Ties Atletico Nacional 2-2 in Supercopa Soccer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, September 24 (Xinhua) -- Beto scored two goals as
Gremio of Brazil rallied to draw with Colombia's Atletico Nacional
2-2 in a Group 4 match of the Supercopa soccer tournament in Porto
Alegre on Tuesday evening.
</P>
<P>
Nacional jumped to a 2-0 lead on goals by Luis Carlos Perea in
the 30th minute and Carlos Castro in the 41st minute.
</P>
<P>
But just when it looked like Gremio would end the first half
without a goal, Beto scored the first goal in the 45th minute.
</P>
<P>
