after Nacional's Dumas Rueda was expelled in the 62nd minute, the
Colombians managed to provide tight coverage.
</P>
<P>
But Beto added second goal in the 79th minute to tie the match.
</P>
<P>
In Group 4, both teams remain without a win. Nacional has a
record of two losses and a tie, while Gremio has tied its three
matches. 
