<HEADLINE> Maradona Backs Striking Chilean Players </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, September 24 (Xinhua) -- Diego Maradona showed his
support on Wednesday to the striking Chilean players for better
working conditions.
</P>
<P>
He also warned similar movements may erupt throughout the South
American region.
</P>
<P>
Maradona is in Chile with his team Boca Juniors for a South
American Supercup match against Chilean champion Colo late
Wednesday.
</P>
