<HEADLINE> China's Production of Railway Vehicles Remains Stable </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 25 (Xinhua) -- China's output of locomotives
reached 1.7 million kw in the first seven months of this year,
down 5.8 percent over the corresponding period in 1996, according
to the latest statistics from State Statistical Bureau.
</P>
